com.ostrichemulators.semtool.util

Class AbstractFileWatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ostrichemulators.semtool.util.AbstractFileWatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FilenameFilter, Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PinningEngineListener, SampleFileWatcher

    public abstract class AbstractFileWatcher
extends Object
implements Runnable, FilenameFilter
    Interface that provides a common protocol for objects that wish to execute code while they are active. Used to filter filenames. Opens up a thread and watches the file.
